        [docReference ISDA FPML version "confirmation-5.13"
            provision "When the public report of this was created or received by this party. If the participant records this time (i.e. it is in the participant\'s party trade information), it will be the time the message was sent. If the execution records this time (i.e. it is in the facility\'s party trade information), it will be the time the message was received."]
